---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Year in Review — 2019"
  description="2019 was ReRoll's most successful year yet. A look back at our highlights, events, and community growth."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-4">

    <!-- Back Navigation -->
    <div class="mb-8">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-sans-ui text-xs tracking-wider uppercase font-bold text-brand-red hover:text-brand-red-dark transition-colors group"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-4 w-4 transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2.5"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
        <span>Back to Table</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 border-b border-dashed border-brand-red/20 pb-8">
      <span class="font-sans-ui text-xs tracking-widest text-brand-red font-bold uppercase">
        Annual Report
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-serif-title text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-red tracking-wide uppercase mt-2 mb-4">
        ReRoll's Year in Review
      </h2>
      <p class="font-serif-body text-base italic text-text-ink-muted mt-2">
        2019 — Our most successful year yet.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Body -->
    <div class="font-serif-body text-base md:text-lg text-text-ink leading-relaxed space-y-10">

      <!-- Intro paragraph -->
      <p class="rulebook-dropcap">
        2019 was ReRoll's most successful year yet. Here's some of the highlights:
      </p>

      <!-- Highlights list -->
      <ul class="space-y-3.5 pl-6 list-none">
        <li class="relative pl-5">
          <span class="absolute left-0 text-brand-red font-bold">❖</span>
          Did our largest event ever with <strong>194 attendees</strong> —&nbsp;
          <a
            href="https://insider.in/international-board-game-day-jun1-2019/event"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-brand-red hover:underline font-bold"
          >International Tabletop Day 2019</a>
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5">
          <span class="absolute left-0 text-brand-red font-bold">❖</span>
          Added&nbsp;
          <a href="https://forum.reroll.in/u/ishira_bhattacharya" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-red hover:underline font-bold">@Ishira_Bhattacharya</a>
          &nbsp;and&nbsp;
          <a href="https://forum.reroll.in/u/navin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-red hover:underline font-bold">@Navin</a>
          &nbsp;to our core team
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5">
          <span class="absolute left-0 text-brand-red font-bold">❖</span>
          Started a second weekly meetup —&nbsp;
          <a
            href="https://forum.reroll.in/t/heavy-cardboard-wednesdays-go-native-hsr-layout-every-wednesday/39"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-brand-red hover:underline font-bold"
          >Heavy Cardboard Wednesdays</a>
          &nbsp;in HSR Layout
        </li>
        <li class="relative pl-5">
          <span class="absolute left-0 text-brand-red font-bold">❖</span>
          Launched the&nbsp;
          <a href="https://forum.reroll.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-red hover:underline font-bold">ReRoll Forums</a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        In July 2019 we moved entirely to online ticketing for all of our events.
        While initially this was met with some resistance, everyone eventually seems to have gotten onboard with the idea.
        This has substantially eased our accounting and logistics hassles.
      </p>

      <p>
        One of the upsides of having all our ticketing and check-ins digital is that we now have a much better understanding
        of our audience profile. While we don't have all of 2019's data digitally, we've put together some data that we
        thought would be useful to share with the community.
      </p>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 my-8">
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
        <span class="text-brand-red text-xs">❖</span>
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section: Attendance -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="font-serif-title text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-red tracking-wide uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-brand-red/60 text-sm">✦</span> How Many People Attended Our Events
        </h3>
        <div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xs border border-brand-red/10 bg-brand-red-pale/30">
          <iframe
            width="100%"
            height="468"
            seamless
            frameborder="0"
            scrolling="no"
            src="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT-iHivuabYbjanTJw56-P-gcEPRFSqpBEawOxehh0N-rxEoRLrNm0pfvqSEceagNSokUs8Ay5sbq8f/pubchart?oid=2107508065&format=interactive"
            title="Event attendance chart"
            class="block w-full"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 my-8">
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
        <span class="text-brand-red text-xs">❖</span>
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section: Advance Tickets -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="font-serif-title text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-red tracking-wide uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-brand-red/60 text-sm">✦</span> How Much in Advance People Buy Tickets
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xs border border-brand-red/10 bg-brand-red-pale/30">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="468"
              seamless
              frameborder="0"
              scrolling="no"
              src="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT-iHivuabYbjanTJw56-P-gcEPRFSqpBEawOxehh0N-rxEoRLrNm0pfvqSEceagNSokUs8Ay5sbq8f/pubchart?oid=1485080994&format=interactive"
              title="Ticket purchase advance time chart"
              class="block w-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xs border border-brand-red/10 bg-brand-red-pale/30">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="371"
              seamless
              frameborder="0"
              scrolling="no"
              src="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT-iHivuabYbjanTJw56-P-gcEPRFSqpBEawOxehh0N-rxEoRLrNm0pfvqSEceagNSokUs8Ay5sbq8f/pubchart?oid=559255711&format=interactive"
              title="Ticket purchase advance time chart 2"
              class="block w-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 my-8">
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
        <span class="text-brand-red text-xs">❖</span>
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section: Show-up times -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="font-serif-title text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-red tracking-wide uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-brand-red/60 text-sm">✦</span> When People Show Up at Our Weekly Meetups
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xs border border-brand-red/10 bg-brand-red-pale/30">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="371"
              seamless
              frameborder="0"
              scrolling="no"
              src="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT-iHivuabYbjanTJw56-P-gcEPRFSqpBEawOxehh0N-rxEoRLrNm0pfvqSEceagNSokUs8Ay5sbq8f/pubchart?oid=968300549&format=interactive"
              title="Weekly meetup arrival times chart"
              class="block w-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xs border border-brand-red/10 bg-brand-red-pale/30">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="371"
              seamless
              frameborder="0"
              scrolling="no"
              src="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT-iHivuabYbjanTJw56-P-gcEPRFSqpBEawOxehh0N-rxEoRLrNm0pfvqSEceagNSokUs8Ay5sbq8f/pubchart?oid=1935564046&format=interactive"
              title="Weekly meetup arrival times chart 2"
              class="block w-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 my-8">
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
        <span class="text-brand-red text-xs">❖</span>
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section: Repeat Rates -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="font-serif-title text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-red tracking-wide uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-brand-red/60 text-sm">✦</span> Repeat Rates of Our Attendees
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xs border border-brand-red/10 bg-brand-red-pale/30">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="371"
              seamless
              frameborder="0"
              scrolling="no"
              src="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT-iHivuabYbjanTJw56-P-gcEPRFSqpBEawOxehh0N-rxEoRLrNm0pfvqSEceagNSokUs8Ay5sbq8f/pubchart?oid=1541732700&format=interactive"
              title="Repeat attendee rate chart"
              class="block w-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xs border border-brand-red/10 bg-brand-red-pale/30">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="371"
              seamless
              frameborder="0"
              scrolling="no"
              src="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT-iHivuabYbjanTJw56-P-gcEPRFSqpBEawOxehh0N-rxEoRLrNm0pfvqSEceagNSokUs8Ay5sbq8f/pubchart?oid=1388444936&format=interactive"
              title="Repeat attendee rate chart 2"
              class="block w-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 my-8">
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
        <span class="text-brand-red text-xs">❖</span>
        <div class="h-[1px] w-full bg-brand-red/20"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Closing note -->
      <p class="italic bg-brand-red-pale border border-brand-red/10 p-5 rounded-xs leading-relaxed text-center">
        We're looking forward to building on this platform and growing the board game hobby in India even further in 2020!
      </p>

      <!-- Community CTA -->
      <p class="text-center font-serif-body text-base text-text-ink-muted">
        Is there any other interesting data you'd like for us to pull up? Let us know 👇
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
